quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  19,12,"Ko an yo Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, Men Okki mo √Ďee√Īal ko o suka"
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka Amen ko o laa…ďu…óo o laatike huloowo [Alla]"
  19,14,Ko o …óiggan…óo jibim…ďe mo …ďen o wanaali ndunndarankeejo ngeddo
  19,15,Kisiyee e makko √Īalnde o jibinaa e √Īalnde o maayata e √Ďalnde o immintintee ko o wuuru…óo
  19,16,"JaŇčto ka Deftere Mariyama tuma nde o wo…ó…óitinoo immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyankoore"
  19,17,"O jogitii gaanin ma…ď…ďe wirngallo, Men Nuli e makko Ruuhu Amen o nanndintinanii mo e …ďanndinke fotondir…óo"
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii Yurmetee…óo On immorde e maa…óa si tawii a laatike ko a kulo [Alla]"
  19,19,"O wi'i: \"Pellet, min ko mi Nulaa…óo Joomi maa…óa fii yo mi okke suka laa…ďu…óo"
  19,20,"O wi'i: \"Ko honno laatoranta lam suka hara …ďanndinke meemaali lam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"
  19,21,"O wi'i: \"ko nii Joomi maa…óa Daaliri: \"∆äum no newii e Am e fii yo Men wa…óu mo Maande fii yim…ďe …ďen e Yurmeende immornde e Amen …óum laatike fiyaake √Ďaawaa…óo"
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure wo…ó…óitiinde"
  19,23,"Ňäata(qatwere) on fi…ói mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: \"Ee hara nun mi maayuno ko adii …óum mi laatoo huunde yejjitaande"
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wata a suno gom…óii Joomi maa…óa wa…óii ley maa…óa caangol"
  19,25,Ye∆īu(dimmbu) faade e maa…óa jullere tamarohi kin nde li…ďa e maa…óa …ďenndu…óe te…ďetee…óe
